HEADWORD: candidiasis
<hw>candidiasis</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an infection caused by fungi of
the genera <gen>Monilia</gen> or <gen>Candida</gen>, especially
<spn>Candida albicans</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> moniliasis, monilia disease.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Candidly</ent>⟦br⟧
